Option 1: pip3 install mpi4py==3.1.4 --no-cache-dir and rest 
Option 2:  pip3 install -r dlio_benchmark/requirements.txt


Note: the connda channel is very crucial for installing packages. 
default channel sometimes creates issues during installation, use conda-forge instead. 
